(a) Fluorescence spectra of a2-GQDs/PBA solution with different glucose concentrations. (b) Fluorescence change (F/F
                        0
                     ) of a2-GQDs/PBA on the glucose concentration ranging from 0-40 mM. F and F0 are the fluorescence intensity of a-GQDs/PBA in the presence and absence of glucose, respectively. (inset shows the photograph image of a2-GQDs/PBA with different glucose concentration under UV irradiation). (c) The fluorescence change of a–GQDs/PBA in the presence of various interfering species (inset shows the photograph image of a2-GQDs/PBA with various interfering species under UV irradiation). (d) Fluorescence decay of a2–GQDs, a2-GQDs/PBA, and a2-GQDs/PBA in the presence of glucose.
